title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 28 2021

description:
Congressman Jim Jordan on budget, debt ceiling, potential gov't shutdown, border crisis, Biden's lies, Durham probe, Jan. 6th investigation, 2022 election. McKenzie and Milley testify, contradict Biden on Afghanistan withdrawal. Psaki answers on tax hikes, budget show she has no understanding of basic business. Greta Thunberg mocks Biden on climate change.
